ed3fbc5c84372b263ae4f2caca6bffe1614","tid":2138562,"uid":5125,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T16:55:50.000Z","msg":"再唔走<br />\n一齊入集中營啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd24abee970cf34987e899b7b9ea07ce28054b15","tid":2138562,"uid":63157,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T16:55:54.000Z","msg":"句update只係point form黎<br />\n大家睇下內文先<br />\n如果你無bno, 你係要同你屋企一齊去before你拎到個bno visa<br />\n<br />\nYou&rsquo;ll also need to show evidence of any non-BN(O) dependants&rsquo; family links to you and <span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">you should travel together to the UK as a family unit</span></strong></span>. A dependant is any of the following:<br />\n<br />\n-spouse or civil partner<br />\n-unmarried partner<br />\n-child (under the age of 18 when they first applied)<br />\n-other family members where they can show there is a high level of dependency"},{"pid":"a45e799cff14e6f0037ef160866dbb5e50b54844","tid":2138562,"uid":243455,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T16:56:09.000Z","msg":"今次真係變走難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad5cb70b3d2648e62bdfedc719f62444c6c08ffd","tid":2138562,"uid":52228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b367e37f9dc552915c5f8de6c820077e08b9d9eb","tid":2138562,"uid":353267,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"054ca55bda0fc9bdb3fe0c613fee8b856ad55eb8","tid":2138562,"uid":52228,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T16:49:37.000Z","msg":"真係俾我講中<br />\n叫人盡快走"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T16:53:41.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">根本國際社會嘅反應 直頭係二戰之前 叫猶太人走嘅態度</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T16:57:55.000Z","msg":"我之前喺第二個post講<br />\nBNO guideline 第十三頁已經叫人apply BNO visa once it&rsquo;s available 根本就係暗示叫人盡快走<br />\n<br />\n講真突然間全世界都開放俾香港人走<br />\n香港遲下一定係會變成人間煉獄先至會咁做<br />\n仲要而家係武肺經濟又差喎<br />\n唔係有人道危機點會開咁多門俾香港人走"}]}